dc_title_s: Sections A, B, & C: Plan of Lots on Money Island, Lands of Stites and Bateman Downe Township - Cumberland County New Jersey
dc_description_s: Section A covers area from Nantuxent Creek to Nantuxent Point. Map shows the property lots along Bayview Road, the property line, and division gut. Also shown is the approximate MLW Line and a part of section B. |Section B shows lots 1 to 25 along Nantuxent Creek. Map shows property lots, proposed new road, Nantuxent Creek, Newport Neck to Nantuxent Creek Road, and part of Section A.|Section C shows Money Island along Nantuxent Creek. Map shows real estate lots, mean high water line, proposed new road, and a part of section B.
